# Urgent Reminders

Small heartbeat-readable list for time-sensitive reminders that shouldn't get lost in general memory.

Format rules:
- Keep entries explicit and normalized.
- `remind_after` is an absolute local timestamp in `{{timezone}}` when possible.
- `repeat` can be: none | daily | weekdays | weekly.
- `last_alerted` is updated when a reminder is actually sent.
- Mark `status: done` instead of deleting if completion timing matters.

